com.viaoa.html

Class OALink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.html.OAHtmlComponent
      • com.viaoa.html.OALink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAImage

    public class OALink
extends OAHtmlComponent
    OALink: Example 
        [Java Code]
    OALink lnk = new OALink("test.html"); 
    form.add("cmdTest", lnk);
    ....
    [HTML Code]
    <A HREF="<%=form.getLink("lnkTest").getHref()%"> <%=form.getLink("lnkTest").getScript()%">>Test link</A>
    -or-
    <A HREF="<%=form.getTable("tabName").getRowLink("lnkTest",row).getHref()%>"<%=form.getTable("tabName").getRowLink("lnkTest",row).getScript()%>>Test link</A>
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
